data.description: YOU’LL ABSOLUTELY LOVE THIS 2 BEDROOM, 2 ½ BATH, 1 CAR GARAGE TOWNHOME IN WONDERFUL CARROLLWOOD VILLAGE! Ideally located close to the Veteran’s Expressway and other major roadways, this delightful 1468 sqft residence offers a tranquil setting that will take you away from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Rich tilework and fine faux wall/ceiling finishes provide a plush, elegant appeal. Your kitchen features stainless steel appliances, crown molding, quartz counters and beautiful cherry wood cabinetry. The splendid breakfast bar is complemented by a spacious dining area. You’ll enjoy the large living room with brand new carpeting and its immediate access to the surprisingly spacious lanai deck with hot tub! Upstairs you’ll find an exceptional master suite with walk-in closet, lovely bath and exquisite custom vanity. Full guest bath boasts a lavish vanity, faux wall finishes and attractive tilework. You’ll appreciate the fine common areas, covered deck and large community swimming pool. Super LOW HOA only $156 per month and includes: grounds and exterior maintenance, landscaping, mowing, irrigation, community pool and painting reserves. Walk, jog or ride a bike over to the AMAZING Carrollwood Village Park ($10 million facility) with Playground, Splash Pad, Dog Park, Picnic Shelters, Paved walking trails, skate park, Ping Pong, Corn hole, Fishing, Fitness equipment and Challenge Course - Fun for the whole family! Minutes away from Tampa International Airport. Everything you’ll need is within a sort, easy drive. Great location and excellent value!
